structure.unit: AGRICULTURAL SEEDS, FEEDING STUFFS, AND FERTILIZERS

law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 370, sec. 15, effective April 8, 1994; amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 333, sec. 10, effective April 8, 1994. -- Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 137, sec. 1, effective July 14, 1992; and ch. 200, sec. 3, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 342, sec. 1, effective July 1, 1982. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 1. -- Amended 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 3, sec. 1. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 160, sec. 3. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1376b-15.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Label requirements -- Seal of certification -- Prohibitions against sale of uncertified tobacco or winter rape (Canola) seeds or of uncertified tobacco seedlings.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/94). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 370 prevails over its amendment in 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 333.
